17:40.310 --> 17:41.520
[Paige laughs]

17:41.520 --> 17:43.605
♪

17:43.605 --> 17:45.065
[sighs deeply]

17:45.065 --> 17:51.029
♪

17:56.118 --> 17:57.035
[sighs]

17:57.035 --> 18:03.000
