- It's not up to your mother.

23:04.259 --> 23:05.928
I gotta make my own way, son.

23:05.928 --> 23:07.054
I gotta get a job.

23:07.054 --> 23:08.597
I've gotta find a place to live.

23:09.264 --> 23:10.891
And I gotta make my own money.

23:11.975 --> 23:16.313
If I don't do this,
I will never be able to trust myself.

23:17.356 --> 23:18.440
Come on, man.
[Finn sobbing]

23:21.610 --> 23:23.111
Come on. Come on.

23:24.696 --> 23:26.156
Okay, I'm gonna,
I'm gonna go get my stuff.

23:27.324 --> 23:28.367
[exhales]

23:28.367 --> 23:29.868
I go-- I gotta get my stuff.

23:29.868 --> 23:30.994
Imma go get my stuff.

23:32.162 --> 23:33.247
Mom, he's--

23:33.247 --> 23:34.414
PAIGE:
It's okay. It's okay.

23:34.414 --> 23:35.541
He's not going forever.

23:35.541 --> 23:36.583
He's just going for now.

23:36.583 --> 23:37.876
